Nokia ovi suite is a computer program available for Microsoft Windows that allows nokia users to backup the contents of their phones to the PC (in .nbu format), install maps on the phone, [[tethering]]<ref>http://europe.nokia.com/support/download-software/nokia-ovi-suite/howto/connect-your-computer-to-the-web-with-nokia-ovi-suite</ref> (phone acts as a modem to connect the computer to the Internet), updating the phone software<ref>http://europe.nokia.com/support/download-software/nokia-ovi-suite/howto/download-and-install-new-software</ref>, among other things. It will replace [[Nokia PC Suite]]<ref>[http://europe.nokia.com/support/download-software/nokia-ovi-suite/faq#00 Nokia Ovi Suite - FAQ]</ref> and is integrated with the [[Ovi (Nokia)|"ovi"]] brand of services.
